{"id:": "/div[1]", "tag": "div", "attributes": {"type": "article", "{http://www.w3.org/XML/1998/namespace}id": "MG-1678-01_276", "resp": "mercure"}, "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/head[1]", "tag": "head", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/head[1]/text()[1]", "text": "[Vers de Madame de Villedieu]"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/bibl[1]", "tag": "bibl", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/bibl[1]/title[1]", "tag": "title", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/bibl[1]/title[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Mercure galant"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/bibl[1]/text()[1]", "text": ", janvier 1678 [tome 1], p. 276-280."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[1]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Vous ne serez point fâchée sans-doute d’entendre aujourd’huy parler de la Justice au lieu de luy [M"}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[1]/hi[1]", "tag": "hi", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[1]/hi[1]/text()[1]", "text": "r"}], "attributes": {"rend": "sup"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[1]/text()[2]", "text": " Talon Premier Avocat General]. Oyez ce que Madame de Villedieu luy fait dire. Tant d’Ouvrages que nous avons d’elle, écrits avec autant de délicatesse que de netteté, vous donnent une assez forte assurance qu’il ne peut rien partir d’elle, qui ne soit fort digne d’estre écouté."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]", "tag": "quote", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/label[1]", "tag": "label", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/label[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Exclamation"}], "attributes": {"rend": "center"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/label[2]", "tag": "label", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/label[2]/text()[1]", "text": "de la Justice sur le choix que le Roy a fait de Mr Tellier pour estre Chancelier de France."}], "attributes": {"rend": "center"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[1]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[1]/text()[1]", "text": "ENfin, grand Jupiter, voicy le jour heureux,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[2]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[2]/text()[1]", "text": "Où depuis si longtemps aspiroient tous mes vœux."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[3]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[3]/text()[1]", "text": "Je voy l’ordre Eternel qui gouverne la France,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[4]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[4]/text()[1]", "text": "Remplir pour ce cher lieu ma plus douce esperance,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[5]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[5]/text()[1]", "text": "Et ta main conduisant le plus grand de ses Rois,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[6]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[6]/text()[1]", "text": "Le Sage "}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[6]/hi[1]", "tag": "hi", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[6]/hi[1]/text()[1]", "text": "le Tellier"}], "attributes": {"rend": "sc"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[6]/text()[2]", "text": " administrer mes Loix."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[7]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[7]/text()[1]", "text": "Déja quand par les soins que tu prens de la Terre,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[8]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[8]/text()[1]", "text": "Tu fis nommer son Fils Ministre de la Guerre,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[9]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[9]/text()[1]", "text": "Je crûs que pour m’offrir un Empire nouveau,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[10]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[10]/text()[1]", "text": "Tullus Hostilius sortoit de son Tombeau."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[11]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[11]/text()[1]", "text": "Le droit de tout oser, la licence impunie,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[12]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[12]/text()[1]", "text": "Qui d’entre les Guerriers sembloit m’avoit bannie,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[13]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[13]/text()[1]", "text": "Au seul nom de "}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]